1
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:06,480
You see what I mean?

2
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:07,880
You see that?

3
00:00:08,930 --> 00:00:11,291
The right English, the right
draw, perfect position, right?

4
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,640
What do I get?

5
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:16,040
Fats Brown, that's what I get.

6
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,160
Fats Brown!

7
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:18,500
Well, I'm sick of it.

8
00:00:18,970 --> 00:00:20,260
I'm sick of hearing his name.

9
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:22,940
I'm the best pull cue on Randolph Street.

10
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:24,040
Me!

11
00:00:24,210 --> 00:00:25,560
Jesse Carter, and you know that.

12
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:26,820
All right.

13
00:00:27,520 --> 00:00:28,340
All right, Fats was good.

14
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,100
I mean, he was good, right?

15
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:32,880
But he's dead.

16
00:00:33,420 --> 00:00:34,440
You hear me? He's dead.

17
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:36,400
He's been dead for over 15 years.

18
00:00:36,945 --> 00:00:38,785
But every time I turn
around, I hear his name.

19
00:00:41,710 --> 00:00:43,060
Oh, you're pretty good, Jesse.

20
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:44,440
But Fats is better.

21
00:00:44,740 --> 00:00:45,740
Fats is the best.

22
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:46,560
Fats.

23
00:00:46,780 --> 00:00:47,780
Fats.

